WEBVTT

00:03:01.082 --> 00:03:05.342
Can't see the lord in every breath
takes a hen and smashes it.

00:03:12.240 --> 00:03:15.700
It’s unfortunate
that we all have come from the same place

00:03:15.700 --> 00:03:17.559
and have to go back to the same place

00:03:17.559 --> 00:03:19.799
but in between, walls have got built.

00:03:19.800 --> 00:03:25.200
Of caste, creed religion, sect
even gender

00:03:26.490 --> 00:03:28.420
and distances took over.

00:03:28.560 --> 00:03:34.040
Maybe to satisfy the ego
so Kabir goes on to say…